---
title: Chicken with Apple & Onion Pan Sauce plus Creamy Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Carrots
description: Pork embraces fruity flavors like no other protein! Our elevated spin on pork chops and applesauce pairs juicy chops with a sweet and savory apple and caramelized onion pan sauce swirled with a touch of butter. On the side are two more classics: roasted carrots and sour cream mashed potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ccabdabced2ef414e818a9-eccb9bc4.jpeg
